node.text: When we were making videos in my Kitchen 3 or 4 years ago getting 10k comments 500k likes and going viral every week there’s was no dancers making videos on Instagram it almost felt like we were the only dancers on the platform putting up bangers for y’all … but now EVERY DANCER is on this Influencer content dance way and and it’s like mannn we started a wave that the world is on and was ahead of our time no capppp but we remain humble it’s all luv🗣 You don’t gotta like us but respect The Big 3🏆🌍
